		<hr />
		
		
			<div><strong>Are we now producing more aggro?</strong><br />&nbsp;</div>
		
		
		
		<div>I have noticed since the recent patch that my spells seem to generate more aggro.  While clearing to Ikkiniz 1 on Saturday, I was stealing aggro from our tank with a single Thundaka landed at 40%.  For some reason, I am wondering if SCS is currently broken or if they somehow tweaked us to produce even more aggro.  Has anyone noticed this and has anyone brought it to dev's attention?  Considering their stealth nerf of throwing classes, I woudln't be surprised if they hit us with the ugly stick as well.</div>
	</td>
</tr>
