		<div>Aye, I know KT aggro can be weird at times, but I'm comparing apples to apples here.  Before the last patch, I hardly if ever had aggro, since I could toss a thundaka or 2 and be relatively safe on aggro as long as I staggered em.  Now I can't cast a single Thundaka while mobs are alive (unless they have HUGE hps) or I run the risk of generating too much aggro.</div>
	</td>
